com.thinkaurelius.titan.graphdb.query.vertex

Class VertexArrayList

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.thinkaurelius.titan.graphdb.query.vertex.VertexArrayList
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    VertexList, VertexListInternal, Iterable<TitanVertex>

    public class VertexArrayList
extends Object
implements VertexListInternal
    An implementation of VertexListInternal that stores the actual vertex references and simply wraps an ArrayList and keeps a boolean flag to remember whether this list is in sort order.
    Author:
    Matthias Broecheler (me@matthiasb.com)
